  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">
    <p class="text-center text-sm font-medium text-brand-text-light tracking-wide uppercase mb-8">Confiado por empresas innovadoras en LATAM y España</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-10">
      <div class="w-28 h-10 bg-brand-card-alt/50 rounded-lg border border-brand-border flex items-center justify-center text-brand-text-muted text-xs font-medium">Logo</div>
      <div class="w-28 h-10 bg-brand-card-alt/50 rounded-lg border border-brand-border flex items-center justify-center text-brand-text-muted text-xs font-medium">Logo</div>
      <div class="w-28 h-10 bg-brand-card-alt/50 rounded-lg border border-brand-border flex items-center justify-center text-brand-text-muted text-xs font-medium">Logo</div>
      <div class="w-28 h-10 bg-brand-card-alt/50 rounded-lg border border-brand-border flex items-center justify-center text-brand-text-muted text-xs font-medium">Logo</div>
      <div class="w-28 h-10 bg-brand-card-alt/50 rounded-lg border border-brand-border flex items-center justify-center text-brand-text-muted text-xs font-medium">Logo</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Por Qué Elegirnos -->
<section class="bg-brand-bg py-24 border-t border-brand-border">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-text">No hacemos solo páginas web.<br class="hidden sm:block"> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-highlight to-brand-highlight-hover">Construimos herramientas de venta.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- Velocidad y Rendimiento -->
      <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-card-alt/50 border border-brand-border hover:border-brand-highlight/50 hover:bg-brand-card-alt hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-highlight/5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-highlight/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">Velocidad y Rendimiento</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text-light leading-relaxed">Sitios web ultrarrápidos que a Google y a tus usuarios les encantarán. Cada milisegundo cuenta para tu posicionamiento y tus ventas.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Diseño Centrado en el Usuario -->
      <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-card-alt/50 border border-brand-border hover:border-brand-highlight/50 hover:bg-brand-card-alt hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-highlight/5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-highlight/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">Diseño Centrado en el Usuario (UX)</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text-light leading-relaxed">Cada botón y cada sección están pensados para guiar a tu cliente hacia la compra. Diseño estratégico que convierte.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Tecnología Escalable -->
      <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-card-alt/50 border border-brand-border hover:border-brand-highlight/50 hover:bg-brand-card-alt hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-highlight/5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-highlight/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-highlight" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">Tecnología Escalable</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text-light leading-relaxed">Usamos la mejor tecnología para que tu web crezca al mismo ritmo que tu empresa. Sin límites, sin fricciones.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

